title: Jarrod Woodgate has romantic dinner with mystery woman
text:
He's had a bit of a rough trot when it comes to finding The One to spend the rest of his life with.

But that all could be about to change for Bachelor In Paradise's Jarrod Woodgate.

On Tuesday, the 32-year-old posted footage to his Instagram Story of him enjoying a romantic quiet night in with a mystery woman - all to the strains of Good Riddance (Time Of Your Life) by Green Day.

Scroll down for video

Has he finally found The One? Bachelor In Paradise's Jarrod Woodgate (pictured) has posted footage of him and a mystery woman enjoying a romantic dinner to his Instagram Story

At the beginning of the footage, a woman's bare legs are clearly visible as she sits in front of a high protein meal of salmon, assorted steamed greens and what looks to be some sort of sweet potato concoction.

As the camera pans across the table, a bowl of tasty oven baked potatoes comes into frame, followed by a bottle of red and some used dip bowls.

At the end of the video, a mysterious woman's voice can be heard.

Trim pins! At the beginning of the footage, a woman's bare legs are clearly visible as she sat in front of a high protein meal of salmon, assorted steamed greens and what looks to be some sort of sweet potato concoction

Jarrod tagged the video: 'And now for dinner' with the happy emoji with rosy cheeks.

It's been a rough trot for the former reality TV star.

In August, Keira Maguire confirmed she'd called it quits with Jarrod just months after they'd rekindled their relationship.

The couple famously met on Bachelor In Paradise in 2017.

In an Q and A session with her many fans on Instagram at the time, she was asked if she was 'still with that guy from Bachelor in Paradise?'

Keira bluntly replied: 'No, we are not'.

authors: Shannon Shipley For Daily Mail Australia
